plan.md
*.draft.md
TODO.local.md
NOTES.local.md

# =============================================================================
# Root-level Markdown — README only
# Every other root .md (CLAUDE.md, DOSSIER.md, CHANGELOG.md, internal plans,
# etc.) is internal-only and stays out of the public repo. Content markdown
# under content/**/*.md is NOT affected by this rule because the pattern is
# anchored to the repo root with the leading slash.
# =============================================================================
/*.md
!/README.md

# Explicit belt-and-suspenders entries for the internal docs that must
# never escape the local working tree, even if the wildcard above is ever
# loosened by accident.
/CLAUDE.md
/DOSSIER.md
/CHANGELOG.md
/BetterGensan PLan.md
